<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢ -<span class="c5"> إِرْشَادُ الْخَلْقِ إِلَى الْعَمَلِ بِخَبَرِ الْبَرْقِ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي مَطْبَعَةِ الْمُقْتَبَسِ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٣٢٩هـ)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣ -<span class="c5"> الْإِسْرَاءُ وَالْمِعْرَاجُ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي دِمَشْقَ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٣٣١هـ)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٤ -<span class="c5"> أَوَامِرُ مُهِمَّةٌ فِي إِصْلَاحِ الْقَضَاءِ الشَّرْعِيِّ:</span> فِي تَنْفِيذِ بَعْضِ الْعُقُودِ عَلَى مَذْهَبِ الشَّافِعِيَّةِ وَغَيْرِهِمْ، طُبِعَ فِي مَطْبَعَةِ التَّرَقِّي فِي دِمَشْقَ د. ت.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٥ -<span class="c5"> الْأَوْرِدَةُ الْمَأْثُورَةُ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي بَيْرُوتَ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٣٢٠هـ)</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٦ -<span class="c5"> تَارِيخُ الْجَهْمِيَّةِ وَالْمُعْتَزِلَةِ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي صَيْدَا سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٣٢٠هـ)</span> .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٧ - تَعْطِيرُ الْمَشَامِّ فِي مَآثِرِ دِمَشْقِ الشَّامِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٨ -<span class="c5"> تَنْبِيهُ الطَّالِبِ إِلَى مَعْرِفَةِ الْفَرْضِ وَالْوَاجِبِ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي مَطْبَعَةِ وَالِدَةِ عَبَّاسٍ مِصْرَ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٣٢٦هـ)</span> .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٩ -<span class="c5"> جَوَامِعُ الْآدَابِ فِي أَخْلَاقِ الْإِنْجَابِ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي مَطْبَعَةِ السَّعَادَةِ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٣٣٩هـ)</span> .<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١٠ -<span class="c5"> خُطَبٌ:</span> وَهِيَ مَجْمُوعَةُ خُطَبٍ لِلْمُؤَلِّفِ ج طُبِعَ فِي دِمَشْقَ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٣٢٥هـ)</span> .<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١١ -<span class="c5"> حَيَاةُ الْبُخَارِيِّ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي صَيْدَا سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٢٣٠هـ)</span> .<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١٢ -<span class="c5"> دَلَائِلُ التَّوْحِيدِ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي دِمَشْقَ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٢٣٠هـ)</span> .<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١٣ -<span class="c5"> الشَّايُ وَالْقَهْوَةُ وَالدُّخَّانُ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي مِصْرَ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٣٢٠هـ)</span> .<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١٤ -<span class="c5"> شَذْرَةُ السِّيرَةِ الْمُحَمَّدِيَّةِ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي مَطْبَعَةِ الْمَنَارِ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٣٢١هـ)</span> .<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>١٥ -<span class="c5"> شَرَفُ الْأَسْبَاطِ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي دِمَشْقَ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٢٣١هـ)</span> .<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١٦ -<span class="c5"> الطَّائِرُ الْمَيْمُونُ فِي حَلِّ لُغْزِ الْكَنْزِ الْمَدْفُونِ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي دِمَشْقَ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٣٢٢هـ)</span> .<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>١٧ -<span class="c5"> فَتَاوَى مُهِمَّةٌ فِي الشَّرِيعَةِ الْإِسْلَامِيَّةِ:</span> فِي الْمَحَاكِمِ الْعُثْمَانِيَّةِ الْمِصْرِيَّةِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>١٨ -<span class="c5"> الْفَتْوَى فِي الْإِسْلَامِ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي دِمَشْقَ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٣٢٩هـ)</span> .<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>١٩ -<span class="c5"> مَذَاهِبُ الْإِعْرَابِ وَفَلَاسِفَةِ الْإِسْلَامِ فِي الْجِنِّ:</span> طُبِعَ فِي دِمَشْقَ مَطْبَعَةِ الْمُقْتَبَسِ سَنَةَ <span class="c2">(١٣٢٨هـ)</span> .<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>